{"tid":1689815,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"候選人無懼DQ 護集會自由","createTime":"2019-11-03T04:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T04:15:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e2de363179f770b39a04e505e062964c0ff6a525","tid":1689815,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T04:15:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191103/3OWZTWGZB7EQ572RCNRCVZDFTA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191103%2F3OWZTWGZB7EQ572RCNRCVZDFTA%2F&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpLis81FSeaDeH2Oz4vdBzj8%3D&h=fb6bc1d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191103%2F3OWZTWGZB7EQ572RCNRCVZDFTA%2F&h=dd4988fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191103/3OWZTWGZB7EQ572RCNRCVZDFTA/</a><br />\n<br />\n候選人無懼DQ 護集會自由<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/DTUqsH_C1azgutp0JdGCf63_Bao=/802x531/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/C63DYBXB34GFWPAVAKG2FI6JTQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FDTUqsH_C1azgutp0JdGCf63_Bao%3D%2F802x531%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FC63DYBXB34GFWPAVAKG2FI6JTQ.gif&h=1217afc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大批泛民區選候選人昨在維園舉辦選舉聚會，參與市民站滿大半個中央草坪。董立華攝<br />\n<br />\n【抗暴之戰】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方早前向申請昨日維園舉行的「求援國際 堅守自治」集會發出反對通知書，過百名區選民主派候選人隨即宣佈，根據《選舉條例》於維園中央草坪發起選舉聚會。有發起集會候選人表明不會屈服於政權打壓，要與港人同行：「正正因為候選人嘅身份，先要話畀香港人知其實我哋唔驚，我哋唔可以因為要參選或者驚被DQ，然後選擇退縮，我哋要同香港人一齊。」<br />\n<br />\n記者：陳嘉裕<br />\n<br />\n逾百民主派區議會候選人昨午各自抵達維園舉行選舉活動，他們目標一致，就是要以選舉活動，讓市民在打壓下仍可發聲，參選元朗嘉湖北選區的伍健偉及其團隊是發起今次行動的其中一名候選人，伍直言希望藉候選人身份及權利，提供機會讓港人出席集會，並指作為代議士需要為民發聲，認為予渠道市民表達意見是議員天職。<br />\n<br />\n參選富恩的關俊笙斥，警方做法是官逼民反，他們將以一切方式對抗制度，用自己方式表達民意。參選天盛的侯文健亦指，今次藉舉行選舉聚會，讓政府知道市民「五大訴求 缺一不可」的決心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/QK44VJqUmnbpW5YErWL-fBzceXc=/802x645/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/VA7GGIIO6XWVDQ6CY7TOBP3DGQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FQK44VJqUmnbpW5YErWL-fBzceXc%3D%2F802x645%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FVA7GGIIO6XWVDQ6CY7TOBP3DGQ.gif&h=2ee750b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/8D7JUBriphcQN6I01TUH2csvlQ4=/802x645/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/XCKGEZYBJCLJLZDV26JEMJGKDQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F8D7JUBriphcQN6I01TUH2csvlQ4%3D%2F802x645%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FXCKGEZYBJCLJLZDV26JEMJGKDQ.gif&h=f7cefa7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/YByreo23iL8mmdl0M96qLIx7Wiw=/802x658/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/WXT6H53Z4MRVQIYHNSHLCW3V6I.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FYByreo23iL8mmdl0M96qLIx7Wiw%3D%2F802x658%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FWXT6H53Z4MRVQIYHNSHLCW3V6I.gif&h=e797ae26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/vWWx6nujuUs8wA1hFOKQcAe75yk=/802x658/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/ZSBYASRK4MCVE7P4IZVI7MUQY4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FvWWx6nujuUs8wA1hFOKQcAe75yk%3D%2F802x658%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FZSBYASRK4MCVE7P4IZVI7MUQY4.gif&h=88dea9a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n斥警剝奪市民發聲權<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：保時捷播《榮光》警強拖司機落車㩒地押走<br />\n<br />\n瑞華選區的候選人林進直指，「政府無論點樣打壓言論自由都好，我哋香港人係唔會屈服嘅」，並指會帶領街坊由維園行到愛丁堡參與之後的集會。提到有機會被警方拘捕及面對法律風險，林進稱，不論和理非或勇武的活動都會有風險，「正正因為候選人身份，先要話畀香港人知其實我哋唔驚，我哋唔可以因為要參選或者驚被DQ，然後選擇退縮，我哋要同香港人一齊」。<br />\n<br />\n屯門龍門區候選人曾錦榮指，警方拒批不反對通知書的做法剝奪市民發聲的權利，指作為候選人必須發聲，並以《基本法》賦予候選人的權力進行選舉聚會。<br />\n轟政府龍門任擺<br />\n<br />\n被問到會否擔心演變成衝突，曾錦榮指並不擔心，若警方單方面失控則會盡候選人責任隔開街坊，又提到在目前情況下，政府「龍門任佢擺」，他的確有機會因而被DQ，但重申選舉聚會是法例賦予的權利，不擔心有違法風險。<br />\n<br />\n維園區候選人李永財昨也帶同支持者舉行選舉聚會，作為當區候選人，李指維園是街坊經常休憩的地點，故嘗試在此地聚會。他並指，集會是公眾權利，港人絕對有權舉行及參與集會，「作為維園候選人，我要企出嚟捍衞集會自由」。<br />\n<br />\n至於主流泛民政黨如民主黨、公民黨和民協等，雖未有公開表明參與發起選舉聚會，但部份民主派候選人包括民主黨屯門區議員黃麗嫦等都有現身維園。<br />\n<br />\n據知，泛民政黨認為參與相關選舉聚會有機會面對法律風險，故以小心謹慎態度處理，擔心選舉聚會或會成為特區政府日後對候選人秋後算賬把柄，但他們不會阻止候選人參與有關活動。"}]}